<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Still Interested?</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #000000;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .item-preview {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .item-preview img {
      width: 250px;
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .item-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #bfa23a; /* gold */
    }

    .button {
      background-color: #bfa23a; /* gold */
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #999999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Thriftiffy</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hey {{name}},</h2>
    <p>
      You recently showed interest in the item below on Thriftify but haven't completed the purchase yet.
    </p>

    <div class="item-preview">
      <img src="{{itemprice}}" alt="{{itemname}}" />
      <div class="item-title">{{itemname}}</div>
    </div>

    <p>
      Is there any issue placing your order? If you need help, we’re here for you!
    </p>
    <p>
      You can <a href="{{link}}" style="color:green">chat with us on WhatsApp</a> and we'll help you buy the item easily.
      You can also contact the seller directly if you have more questions.
    </p>

    <p>
      Also, don’t forget — use our <strong>₦5,000 OFF coupon code</strong> at checkout!
    </p>

    <a class="button" href="{{sellername}}">Complete Your Purchase</a>

    <p class="footer">
      This message was sent because you expressed interest in an item on Thriftify.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
